Based on your detailed technical specification and brand guidelines, I‚Äôll implement the landing page using React + Tailwind CSS, as it allows full control over structure, responsive behavior, and custom fonts while staying within the allowed libraries.

Since the "Brush" decorative font is referenced but not available via Google Fonts, I‚Äôll simulate its usage by defining a @font-face rule inside a <style> tag (as external font files aren‚Äôt provided). In production, you‚Äôd replace this with the actual font file.

Also note:
