- All colors strictly follow your BrandBoard.
- No external dependencies beyond lucide-react for icons (used sparingly; replaced with SVG if needed, but Lucide supports color customization).
- Forms will have basic validation and simulated submission (no backend).
- SEO meta tags are included in the component‚Äôs return (though in real apps they‚Äôd go in <head> via Helmet‚Äîbut we‚Äôre limited to one JSX file).

Here is the complete App.jsx:

import React, { useState } from 'react';
